{"tid":1925734,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"大埔富亨邨亨泰樓3住戶確診　衞生署憂經喉管播毒　袁國勇、張竹君、徐德義等到場視察","createTime":"2020-03-14T14:50:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-14T15:34:45.000Z","uid":59684,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a2105828689f6fce4d26a61f53f5e9f446b432cd","tid":1925734,"uid":59684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-14T14:50:52.000Z","msg":"不斷更新】大埔富亨邨亨泰樓3住戶確診　衞生署憂經喉管播毒　袁國勇、張竹君、徐德義等到場視察<br />\n2020/3/14 &mdash; 20:39<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAAA<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/90006426_10163654865545019_4008688565872492544_o20copy_PZrjP_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F90006426_10163654865545019_4008688565872492544_o20copy_PZrjP_1200x0.png&h=38681ab9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n衞生署今日公布，本港新增 3 宗確診個案，及 1 宗初步陽性個案，累計確診個案增至 141 宗。其中第 140 宗個案是一名 59 歲男子，住在大埔富亨邨亨泰樓。確診男子因行動不便長期留在家中，但本月 10 日起咳嗽，至今日確診。今午，有身穿保護衣人員到亨泰樓清潔消毒。<br />\n<br />\n衞生署衞生防護中心傳染病處主任張竹君今日在記者會上提到，這名病人和「埃及旅行團」群組第 119 宗及 124 宗夫婦個案，都是居住亨泰樓，而且三人居住單位的座向一樣，都是住在 13 室，但互不相識，擔心大廈有喉管問題導致病毒擴散感染。<br />\n<br />\n富亨邨共有 8 座，於 1990 年入伙，截至去年底共有 1300 戶，人口多達 3100 人，其中亨泰樓為 Y4 型公屋，早前出現同座感染的長康邨康美樓則是 Y2 型設計公屋。 Y4 型公屋有氣喉設計，氣喉與糞渠位於單位廚房，但有門隔開。<br />\n<br />\n根據消防處發佈的訊息，下午 4 時 24 分曾接獲一宗「懷疑感染個案」通報，地址亦是亨泰樓。至 6 時許，有身穿保護衣的漁護署員工，在確診者所住單位撿走一隻巴西龜。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89342310_2925324744219793_3366708809023094784_n_s3wt7_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89342310_2925324744219793_3366708809023094784_n_s3wt7_1200x0.png&h=945f39cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立場新聞記者傍晚到訪確診個案單位樓下同一座向，亦即 33 樓 13 室單位，戶主表示洗手間內的喉管沒有被改裝，目測環境乾淨。<br />\n<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89436554_2925410044211263_4789183470444216320_n_wEAyn_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89436554_2925410044211263_4789183470444216320_n_wEAyn_1200x0.png&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=4d6297b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F89436554_2925410044211263_4789183470444216320_n_wEAyn_1200x0.png&h=2c47b73b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/89436554_2925410044211263_4789183470444216320_n_wEAyn_1200x0.png</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/不斷更新-大埔富亨邨亨泰樓3住戶確診-衞生署憂經喉管播毒-袁國勇-張竹君-徐德義等到場視察/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%A8%E9%82%A8%E4%BA%A8%E6%B3%B0%E6%A8%933%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B6%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E6%86%82%E7%B6%93%E5%96%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B-%E5%BE%90%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F%2F&d=mMkNc61%2FAm5nYK%2BypTXmCf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=072d71e1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E4%B8%8D%E6%96%B7%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0-%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E5%AF%8C%E4%BA%A8%E9%82%A8%E4%BA%A8%E6%B3%B0%E6%A8%933%E4%BD%8F%E6%88%B6%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A1%9E%E7%94%9F%E7%BD%B2%E6%86%82%E7%B6%93%E5%96%89%E7%AE%A1%E6%92%AD%E6%AF%92-%E8%A2%81%E5%9C%8B%E5%8B%87-%E5%BC%B5%E7%AB%B9%E5%90%9B-%E5%BE%90%E5%BE%B7%E7%BE%A9%E7%AD%89%E5%88%B0%E5%A0%B4%E8%A6%96%E5%AF%9F%2F&h=0d94a835\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/不斷更新-大埔富亨邨亨泰樓3住戶確診-衞生署憂經喉管播毒-袁國勇-張竹君-徐德義等到場視察/</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好擔心啲龜</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W8OhKyd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW8OhKyd.jpg&h=8c1993a3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4aZ48ZT